  polygon 24 78 19 68 23 73 17 60 21 64 15 50 19 54 flame
  polygon 22 48 17 36 21 40 15 26 19 30 flame
  polygon 25 26 20 16 23 20 18 6 22 10 flame
  glow radius 3
}

